cubit (0.0.5) unstable; urgency=low

  New features:
  * network (only) support
  * variable framerate
  * 3d display
  * windows builds available once again

  Tweak:
  * combine polygons
  * multithreaded generator
  * glew extension loading

  Bugfixes:
  * some new ones are fixed
  * better physics

